# Product specifications

Specifications own product intent, requirements, acceptance, authority, proof
claims, rollback, and maintenance. Each active SPEC links one schema-valid task
plan; active implementation state belongs in `docs/exec-plans/active/` rather
than being duplicated here. Use [`task-plan.schema.json`](task-plan.schema.json).
Completed or superseded work remains indexed with its successor and evidence
route rather than being silently deleted.
